                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-536" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY LING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I took the prisoner to the station-house, and saw the shawl taken from her pocket.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received an excellent character—the witnesses engaged to provide for her.)</p>
